  "keyFeatures": [
    "Zero-config defaults with JetBrains Mono and macOS font rendering",
    "Built-in AI assistant for error recovery and natural language command generation",
    "Auto dark/light theme switching with macOS system appearance",
    "Curated shell suite with zsh plugins, Starship, Delta, Lazygit, and Yazi",
